@startuml seq-08-footprint
' 序列图8：记录浏览足迹
title 记录浏览足迹序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "article-detail.js" as Front
participant "FootprintController" as Ctrl
participant "FootprintService" as Svc
participant "FootprintMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 进入文章详情页(onLoad)
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/footprint/add(userId,target_type=1,target_id,snapshot_title,snapshot_cover,snapshot_author)
Ctrl -> Svc: add(footprint)
Svc -> Mapper: insert(footprint)
Mapper -> DB: INSERT INTO footprint(user_id,target_type,target_id,snapshot_*,create_time)
DB --> Mapper: 影响行数1
Mapper --> Svc: footprint_id
Svc --> Ctrl: 成功
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200}
Front -> Front: 静默成功(不打扰用户)

@enduml
